[vc_column_text css=”” css_animation=”bottom-to-top”]

Due to Launch in 2024

[/vc_column_text]

[vc_column_text css_animation=”bottom-to-top”]

ASNU’s Digital Flow Kit is an exciting new add-on kit that can work with any ASNU Classic GDI machine to enable more accurate & speciﬁc measuring when testing fuel injectors. The standard kit includes all the hardware and the software programme, with optional future add-ons/upgrades available.[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=”.vc_custom_1581597772628{margin-top: 55px !important;}”][vc_column offset=”vc_col-md-6″][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1712656674655{padding-top: 30px !important;}” css_animation=”bottom-to-top”]

ASNU remote Digital Flow Kit

[/vc_column_text]

[vc_column_text]ASNU’s Digital Flow Kit is an exciting new add-on kit that can work with any ASNU Classic GDI machine to enable more accurate & speciﬁc measuring when testing fuel injectors. The standard kit includes all the hardware and the software programme, with optional future add-ons/upgrades available.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column offset=”vc_col-md-6″]
[vc_column_text]*Click to enlarge image[/vc_column_text]
[/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row_content_no_spaces” content_placement=”middle” css=”.vc_custom_1580302432101{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}” el_class=”z-index”][vc_column]

General Features of the Digital Flow Kit
* Available as an upgrade to work with any existing ASNU Classic GDI Machine`(no need for new purchase)
* User defined injector RPM, Duty & Pulse Width
* User defined Flush and Leak test duration
* 8 Individual Injector Select Controls
* Worldwide user interface with icon control
* Save results to file for future reference
* Print test reports for customers (will require external printer)

Touchscreen Windows Tablet & Windows PC Compatible User Interface
* Mount a Windows Tablet on the machine and use the touchscreen
* Or place a Windows PC next to the machine and use a mouse/keypad or touchscreen (if fitted)

Digital Flow Measurement
* No need to drain the flow tubes
* Faster Testing - typically measures the flow of 8 injectors in 30 secs
* Eliminates errors in reading the tube levels
* Eliminates errors from fluid remaining in the tubes
* Measure flows up to 4000cc/min @ 3 bar on ASNU flowrite as standard (up to 8000cc/min as an option)
* Option for injector deadtime measurement
* Option for Injector Short Pulse Adder & Short Pulse Multiplier data generation

Digital Pressure Measurement & Automatic Pressure Control
* High accuracy digital pressure measurement
* BAR or PSI display
* Automatically controls the fuel pressure regardless of the injector flow
* No need to set the pressure with the injector firing in the spray position then moving to the flow tube position - saving time!

Graphical Display of Flows
* Target flow options (use the average flow from the set of injectors under test or a specific flow (e.g. from an injector data sheet)
* Different colours to show injectors out of limits

Fuel Temperature Measurement
* Display in Deg C or Deg F
* Determine the effect of temperature on the injector flow

Software Conversion/Scaling of Flow Results
* Convert from cc/min to lbs/hr & vice versa
* Convert between Flowrite & Gasoline

Automatic Testing Options
* Flow vs Pressure Sweep
* Flow vs Pressure vs Voltage

Injector Electrical Test
* Check for injector coil faults
* Different colours for injectors out of limits
* Target inductance options (use the average inductance from the set of injectors under test or from an injector data sheet

Test Information Data Entry
* Record injector part numbers/serial numbers
* Record vehicle information
* Record customer details
[/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row_content_no_spaces” equal_height=”yes” css=”.vc_custom_1550340774959{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}” el_id=”brightLargeBlocks”][vc_column css_animation=”none” css=”.vc_custom_1550326245867{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-right: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;padding-left: 0px !important;background-color: #f0f4f6 !important;}” el_class=”explore” offset=”vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-12 vc_col-xs-12″]

[vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1550335401941{margin-top: 20px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]

Latest

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1550322294328{margin-top: -20px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]

Technology

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708017457381{padding-top: 5px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]ASNU have now taken their Injector Diagnostics Programme to the next level, where Performance and Racing teams need to know and understand greater the injectors operation and performance, ASNU set the standards and met their requirements.[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][vc_column css_animation=”none” el_class=”explore” offset=”vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-12 vc_col-xs-12″ css=”.vc_custom_1550334712529{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;background-color: #f0f4f6 !important;}”]

[vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708017375591{margin-top: 20px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]

UK Manufactured

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708017413897{margin-top: -20px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]

Built to Last

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1714055074664{padding-top: 5px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]ASNU are the global leader in the Testing & Servicing of gasoline injectors for the automotive industry. With over 30 years of experience, our continued investment R&D has resulted in major partnerships across the automotive sector. ASNU offer a range of systems to suit all markets.[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][vc_column css_animation=”none” el_class=”explore” offset=”vc_col-lg-4 vc_col-md-12 vc_col-xs-12″ css=”.vc_custom_1550334750174{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;background-color: #f0f4f6 !important;}”]

[vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708349691543{margin-top: 20px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]

Projetos Especiais

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708349733379{margin-top: -20px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]

Performance

[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=”.vc_custom_1708349459196{padding-top: 5px !important;}” css_animation=”none”]Our investment in R&D has taken our Injector Diagnostics Programme to the next level, where Performance and Racing teams need to understand and diagnose the injectors operation and performance and ASNU set the standards in this demanding environment[/vc_column_text]

[/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row_content_no_spaces” equal_height=”yes” css=”.vc_custom_1501247507416{margin-bottom: 0px !important;}”][vc_column css_animation=”none” css=”.vc_custom_1550324610280{margin-bottom: 0px !important;background-image: url(https://asnu.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/7_mini-1.jpg?id=18) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}” offset=”vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-xs-12″]
[/vc_column][vc_column css_animation=”none” css=”.vc_custom_1708343305198{background-color: #0094ce !important;}” offset=”vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-xs-12″]

The ASNU Classic GDI:
Test and Service Every Gasoline Injector ever produced!. K-JET/PORT/SIDE-FEED/TOP FEED/MONOPOINT/GDI/SOLENOID/PIEZO
